review_blob: Sweet Aroma, excellent taste (carmel, toast & butterscotch). Very excellent brew by the Goose. Enjoyed with wife!

beer_brewer_name: Schneider Weisse G. Schneider & Sohn GmbH
review_blob: Freeze out the water and eisbock you have! Tried on draft. Incredibly smooth, very flavorful & complex. True Bavarian Hefe and then some (abv+++). Worth its weight in gold and one of my favorites.
